Subject: [PATCH v2 1/2] Staging: fbtft: Fix probing of gpio descriptor
Date:   Tue, 16 Jul 2019 08:24:36 +0800
Message-Id: <1563236677-5045-2-git-send-email-preid@electromag.com.au>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 1.8.3.1
